metadata.name: Nidranauts2 #1
metadata.description: Nidranauts are cosmic dream travelers who traverse the Dreams Sphere to communicate symbols, stories, and transmissions. The shapeshifting Nidranauts resonate meaning according to codes of synchronicity within each dreamer. The Nidranauts NFTs are a unique collection of 10,800 artworks created from dreams and expanded awareness. Simultaneous knowing, lucid awareness, and synesthesia are the qualities and characteristics of the shift into the DreamSphere phase of consciousness.
